<Body>
	<Title>山西新绛民办中学74名学生集体食物中毒</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2007年8月17日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">新华社</Participant><Location lid="l1">太原</Location><Time tid="t1" type="absTime">2007年8月16日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">信息</Denoter></Event>：（记者 刘云伶）</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e2"><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">16日2时</Time>起，<Location lid="l2">山西新绛县海泉中学</Location><Participant sid="s2">74名学生</Participant><Denoter did="d2" type="action">出现</Denoter><Object oid="o2">食物中毒症状</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e3">陆续被<Denoter did="d3" type="movement">送到</Denoter><Location lid="l3">当地医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e4"><Denoter did="d4" type="operation">救治</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e5">目前仍有<Participant oid="o5" type="recipient">20余名学生</Participant>在<Location lid="l5">医院</Location>接受<Denoter did="d5" type="operation">观察</Denoter></Event>和<Event eid="e6"><Denoter did="d6" type="operation">治疗</Denoter></Event></Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e7"><Participant sid="s7">记者</Participant>从山西省教育厅<Denoter did="d7" type="statement">了解</Denoter>到</Event>，海泉中学是运城市新绛县一所较大的民办中学，<Event eid="e8"><Time tid="t8" type="timeInterval">近日起</Time><Participant sid="s8">部分学生</Participant>提前<Denoter did="d8" type="operation">开学</Denoter></Event>并<Event eid="e9"><Denoter did="d9" type="action">住校</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e10"><Time tid="t10" type="relTime">16日2时许</Time>，<Participant sid="s10">74名高中学生</Participant>陆续<Denoter did="d10" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>呕吐等<Object oid="o10">症状</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e11">之后被<Denoter did="d11" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l11" type="destination">新绛县两所医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e12">接受<Denoter did="d12" type="operation">救治</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e13">初步被<Denoter did="d13" type="operation">诊断</Denoter>为食物中毒。</Event></Sentence></Paragraph>
      
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e14"><Time tid="t14" type="relTime">8时许</Time>，<Participant sid="s14">新绛县卫生局和防疫部门</Participant>对这起食物中毒事件进行了<Denoter did="d14" type="operation">调查</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e15">初步认定为<Participant sid="s15">学生</Participant>因食物不洁引发<Denoter did="d15" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e16">随即对<Object oid="o16">学校的饭厅</Object>进行<Denoter did="d16" type="operation">查封</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
 
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e17"><Participant sid="s17">山西省教育厅体卫处负责人</Participant><Denoter did="d17" type="statement">告诉</Denoter><Participant oid="o17">记者</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e18"><Time tid="t18" type="relTime">目前</Time><Participant sid="s18">多数学生</Participant>已<Denoter did="d18" type="movement">离</Denoter><Location lid="l18">院</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">20余名学生</Participant>仍在接受<Denoter did="d19" type="operation">观察治疗</Denoter></Event>，病情基本稳定。</Sentence><Sentence>据了解，<Event eid="e20"><Participant sid="s20">卫生部门</Participant>已对<Participant oid="o20">发病学生</Participant>进行<Denoter did="d20" type="operation">采样</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e21"><Participant sid="s21" type="agent">山西省教育厅</Participant>已就此事向<Participant oid="o21" type="recipient">全省学校</Participant>进行<Denoter did="d21" type="statement">通报</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e22">并全面<Denoter did="d22" type="operation">排查</Denoter>学校食品安全<Object oid="o22">隐患</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
